namespace = page_events

country_event = {
	id = page_events.0
	title = page_events.0.t
	desc = page_events.0.d
	picture = TRADEGOODS_eventPicture
	is_triggered_only = yes

	option = {
		name = page_next
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = page_events.0 } }
	}

	option = {
		name = page_previous
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = page_events.0 } }
	}

	option = {
		name = category_events.0.Events
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = category_events.28 } }
	}

	option = {
		name = category_events.0.Kheterata
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = category_events.57 } }
	}

	option = {
		name = category_events.0.x
	}
}
